Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Time to Depart -\NThe Land of Wano and the Straw Hats"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These rice dumplings are yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This red-bean soup is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish, meat, and vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all good! You gotta try them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little while ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RUINS OF ODEN CASTLE, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the place where Kozuki Oden,\NKin'emon, and the others' graves once were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GRAVE OF KOZUKI ODEN\NVASSAL KANJURO     KOZUKI MOMONOSUKE\NVASSAL KIN'EMON     VASSAL RAIZO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ruins of Oden Castle, Kuri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ODEN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was blown away without a trace\Nby Kaido's Blast Breath...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's where Oden built his first castle\Nafter he became the Daimyo of Kuri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daimyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffytaro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! What brought you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to tell Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other things\Nthat we want to tell him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you-{\i1}gara{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} would be happy\Nto see the man who saved the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Luffytaro-{\i1}dono{\i0} and the others here,\Nwe were able to bring down Orochi and Kaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take back the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nwho became the Shogun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we promise you that we will\Nreturn this country to what it once was,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Ashura and Izo were here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our hearts, along with Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're having a banquet\Nin the afterlife now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purr-meow-meow-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oden{\i0} cooked by Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nwas the most delicious thing in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the taste of {\i1}oden{\i0}\Nthat we had together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It tasted even better\Nafter we trained with Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! I wish I could eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nto cook it for us sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should stock up on\Ningredients for it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please! Buy lots of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we all would like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we saying goodbye already? No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna say goodbye to Nami!\NNo, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Carrot...\N--What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Mokomo Dukedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect our home\Nwith Wanda and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyagi! Tristan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for teaching me\Nmedicine and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chopper, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, Carrot-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you snuck onto the Sunny\Nbecause you wanted to see the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to see islands\NI didn't know about and meet nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:08:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of scary moments,\Nbut I feel a little stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the adventure I had with you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I'll treasure\Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do one last Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun chatting and having a good time\Nwith you in the women's quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy, Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I saw Zoro on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,YASUIE     PEDRO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PEDRO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,YASUIE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,YASUIE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to have a drink with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pour it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lay the flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro-{\i1}san{\i0}, you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,YASUIE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the nice temple is built,\NI'll come to see you every day, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're not gonna be lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,YASUIE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here. Does that mean\Nthe time has come for you to depart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I have to say goodbye\Nto my father's beloved Enma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, when I fought Kaido with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Rope Dragon Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Oden's sword, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido must have sensed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enma that can even cut through\Nthe bottom of hell..." Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed with Oden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he had\Ncompletely mastered this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you saved the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by skillfully wielding Enma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it looks as if Enma is rejoicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to have a new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's this, Kid Fra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me if I could check on\Nthe places where you repaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to help you out,\Nyou dumb shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perr-fect! You thankless pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have left me\Nat least one spot to fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you repaired it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd expected from\Nthe Straw Hats' shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! You simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,DRAPER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, yes! I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--It really looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usohachi-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the most handsome man\Nin the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, do you want something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't need to tell me.\NI know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This color looks good on you, too!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usohachi-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N--Hey! Lady killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man\Nwho was made to wear the color red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, don't fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I mean, no, no!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need plain black cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Black cloth?\NWhat are you going to use that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will provide you with the finest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sangoro's Special Soba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SPECIAL SOBA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's good!\N--I love the Special Soba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you for the meal.\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, you little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't properly thanked you yet\Nfor saving me at Onigashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.\NI just did what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, will you come back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Sangoro-{\i1}san{\i0}'s soba\Nmakes me want to work hard tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sangoro-{\i1}san{\i0}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a hot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I have one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OKOBORE TOWN, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take a break\Nand have some red-bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you always\Nfor the refreshments, Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RED-BEAN SOUP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's red-bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum, yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}'s red-bean soup is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Eat the rice cake, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that\NI have to say goodbye to you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lump in my throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, then Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people I love leave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me your precious rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget about\NBig Bro and the others, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you and Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:32.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TOKAGE PORT, UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back to the present...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really made it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't guarantee it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Thanks, Dr. Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! We're ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you really sure\Nabout leaving like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:21:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't say goodbye\Nto Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0} and Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold, Mosshead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Twirly Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of all the people in the Land of Wano,\Nthey shared the most adventures with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe it's a little sad\Nto just leave like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll come!
